'''古尔冈快速地铁'''（简称：快速地铁）是[[印度|印度]][[哈里亚纳邦|哈里亚纳邦]][[古尔冈|古爾岡市]]的[[中型铁路系统|中运量城市轨道交通系统]]。<ref name="Railway gazette">{{cite web | url = http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/rapid-metrorail-gurgaon-opens.html | title = Rapid MetroRail Gurgaon opens | publisher = [[Railway_Gazette_International|Railway Gazette]] | date = 2013-11-15 | accessdate = 2014-12-28 | archive-date = 2018-04-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180426144645/http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/rapid-metrorail-gurgaon-opens.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Total Rail">{{cite web | url = http://www.totalrail.org/2013/11/18/rapid-metrorail-gurgaon-launched/ | title = Rapid MetroRail Gurgaon launched | publisher = Total Rail | author = Simon Crompton-Reid | date = 2013-11-18 | accessdate = 2014-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141228122939/http://www.totalrail.org/2013/11/18/rapid-metrorail-gurgaon-launched/ | archivedate = 2014-12-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="subways.net">{{cite web | url = http://www.subways.net/india/gurgaon.html | title = Gurgaon automated metro | accessdate = 2014-12-28 | archive-date = 2017-09-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170920052957/http://www.subways.net/india/gurgaon.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/gurgaon/metro-lines-cover-only-3-of-gurugram/articleshow/70905439.cms|title=Metro lines cover only 3% of Gurugram|accessdate=2020-03-04|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831131021/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/gurgaon/metro-lines-cover-only-3-of-gurugram/articleshow/70905439.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>本系统可在{{tsl|en|Sikandarpur metro station|西坎达普尔站|西坎达普尔站}}与[[德里地铁|德里地铁]][[德里地铁黄线|黄线]]换乘。古尔冈快速地铁由德里地铁有限公司（DMRC）运营，两者共享票务系统，因此古尔冈快速地铁被视为德里地铁的一部分。

该系统起初由古尔冈快速地铁有限公司（RMGL）建造和运营，是世界上第一个完全由私人融资的现代化城市轨道交通系统。该合资企业没有接受来自印度联邦政府、哈里亚纳邦政府或任何公共部门的投资。古尔冈快速地铁是印度第一个拍卖其车站命名权的系统。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/mumbai-metro-joins-station-branding-ride-114041600482_1.html|title=Mumbai Metro joins station branding ride|first=Anusha|last=Soni|date=2014-04-19|publisher=|via=Business Standard|access-date=2020-03-04|archive-date=2020-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304071113/https://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/mumbai-metro-joins-station-branding-ride-114041600482_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2019年9月，{{tsl|en|Infrastructure Leasing & Financial Services|IL&FS}}（原RMGL大股东）宣布由于公司的财务问题，没有足够的资源继续运行快速地铁，并正在寻找另一个实体来资助和接管业务。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://urbantransportnews.com/gurgaon-rapid-metro-is-in-trouble-may-stop-operations-from-september/|title=Gurgaon Rapid Metro is in trouble, may stop operations from September|last=News|first=Urban Transport|date=2019-08-26|website=Urban Transport News|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-27|archive-date=2020-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200506091308/https://www.urbantransportnews.com/gurgaon-rapid-metro-is-in-trouble-may-stop-operations-from-september/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 在与哈里亚纳邦政府发生短暂纠纷以及[[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]]和哈里亚纳邦高等法院的判决后，德里地铁公司从IL＆FS手中接管了快速地铁的运营。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://urbantransportnews.com/delhi-metro-starts-taking-over-process-of-gurgaon-rapid-metro-from-ilfs/|title=Delhi Metro starts taking over process of Gurgaon Rapid Metro from IL&FS|last=Khare|first=Anushka|date=2019-09-24|website=Urban Transport News|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-27|archive-date=2020-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227030154/https://www.urbantransportnews.com/delhi-metro-starts-taking-over-process-of-gurgaon-rapid-metro-from-ilfs/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==线路==
[[File:Rapid_Transit_Map_of_Delhi.jpg|thumb]]、[[诺伊达地铁|诺伊达地铁]]和古尔冈快速地铁]]
快速地铁分几个阶段建造。一期工程位于西坎德布尔（Sikanderpur）站以北的5.1公里，西坎德布尔站和DLF Phase Ⅱ站之间的路段是双轨，而DLF Phase Ⅱ站以北为单向[[灯泡线|灯泡线]]；二期工程是从西坎德普尔站向南延伸6.6公里，至古尔冈55-56区站，大部分路段位于高尔夫球场路。<ref name=phase2/> 一期工程于2013年11月14日开通；二期工程于2017年3月31日开始投入运营。<ref name=phase2>{{cite web|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/gurgaon/rapid-metro-enters-south-gurgaon-with-launch-of-phase-ii/story-CJahviCCbZSi6QWDkar0SM.html|title=After delays, affluent south Gurgaon hops on to Rapid Metro|last=Kumar|first=Kartik|publisher=[[Hindustan_Times|Hindustan Times]]|date=2017-03-31|accessdate=2017-07-31|archive-date=2017-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401003255/http://www.hindustantimes.com/gurgaon/rapid-metro-enters-south-gurgaon-with-launch-of-phase-ii/story-CJahviCCbZSi6QWDkar0SM.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

快速地铁各车站的长度为75m。作为德里地铁黄线和古尔冈快速地铁的换乘站，西坎德布尔（Sikanderpur）站的换乘通道为90米长，9米宽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rapidmetrorail.com/welcome.html|title=About Us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111015005136/http://rapidmetrorail.com/welcome.html|archivedate=2011-10-15|url-status=dead|accessdate=2011-12-01}}</ref>
