==设施==
由于该系统全高架自动运行<ref name="Rapid MetroRail Gurgaon Limited">{{cite web | url = http://www.rapidmetrogurgaon.com/downloads/Newsletter1.pdf | title = Rapid MetroRail Gurgaon Newsletter 1 | publisher = rapidmetrogurgaon.com | accessdate = 2014-12-28 | archive-date = 2016-04-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160408190540/http://www.rapidmetrogurgaon.com/downloads/Newsletter1.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，因此也被部分铁道杂志定义为[[轻轨|轻轨]]<ref name="Railway gazette"/><ref name="Total Rail"/><ref name="subways.net"/>。
===车辆===
2010年4月21日，[[西门子|西门子]]宣布已获得建造地铁线路的总包合同，其中包括5列3节编组的地铁车辆。<ref name="siemens">{{cite press release | date=12 August 2009 | url=http://www.siemens.com/press/en/pressrelease/2010/mobility/imo20100422.htm | publisher=[[Siemens|Siemens]] | title=Siemens Mobility to equip additional metro line in Delhi | access-date=2020-03-04 | archive-date=2018-04-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180426213112/https://www.siemens.com/press/en/pressrelease/2010/mobility/imo20100422.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref> 这笔车辆的订单事后被西门子分包给中国的[[南车株洲电力机车|南车株洲电力机车]]，以制造5列铝制空调列车。<ref name=trains></ref>中国制造的第一列三节编组车辆于2012年9月11日抵达古尔冈。<ref>{{cite web|title=First set of Rapid Metro Rail coaches arrive in Gurgaon from China|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/rapid-metro-rail-gurgaon-system-metro-rail-service-delhi-metro/1/217107.html|website=India Today|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2016-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329024711/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/rapid-metro-rail-gurgaon-system-metro-rail-service-delhi-metro/1/217107.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 为了应对二期工程的开通，古尔冈快速地铁有限公司额外地订购了7列3节编组的地铁车辆，这7列车辆中的最后4列于2016年2月5日到达古尔冈。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rapid Metro gets all seven new rakes for Phase-2 run - Times of India|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/gurgaon/Rapid-Metro-gets-all-seven-new-rakes-for-Phase-2-run/articleshow/50874081.cms|website=The Times of India|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212043851/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/gurgaon/Rapid-Metro-gets-all-seven-new-rakes-for-Phase-2-run/articleshow/50874081.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

每列车耗资420万美元（3亿卢比），车身为银色和蓝色。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/Haryana/It-s-official-Rapid-Metro-in-6-months/Article1-929596.aspx |title=It's official, Rapid Metro in 6 months |newspaper=Hindustan Times |date=2012-09-14 |accessdate=2013-09-28 |archive-date=2013-01-25 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130125073753/http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/Haryana/It-s-official-Rapid-Metro-in-6-months/Article1-929596.aspx |dead-url=yes }}</ref>一列车的总长度为59.94米，宽为2.8米，每节车厢有4对门，车顶配有空调，每列车可容纳约800位乘客。<ref>{{cite web |author=DVV Media Group GmbH |url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/nc/news/single-view/view/csr-zhuzhou-to-supply-gurgaon-trains.html |title=CSR Zhuzhou to supply Gurgaon trains |work=Railway Gazette |accessdate=2013-09-28 |archive-date=2011-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812140320/http://www.railwaygazette.com/nc/news/single-view/view/csr-zhuzhou-to-supply-gurgaon-trains.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>该地铁的设计运能为每小时运送3万名乘客。<ref name=rgiturnkey>{{cite journal | url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/10/gurgaon-metro-turnkey-contract-awarded-1.html | title=Gurgaon metro turnkey contract awarded | journal=[[Railway_Gazette_International|Railway Gazette International]] | date=2010-04-23 | access-date=2020-03-04 | archive-date=2010-04-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100426115218/http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/10/gurgaon-metro-turnkey-contract-awarded-1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==运营==
===票务===
古尔冈快速地铁的票价为固定的两种价格，第一种是乘客仅在一期工程（或二期工程）路段内乘坐，含Sikanderpur站，票价为20卢比；第二种是乘客从一期工程车站乘至二期工程的车站（反之亦然），也就是说跨过了Sikanderpur站，票价为35卢比。<ref>{{cite web |last=Banerjee |first=Rumu |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/news-by-industry/transportation/railways/delhi-metro-to-link-up-with-rapid-rail/articleshow/15372304.cms |title=Delhi Metro to link up with Rapid Rail - The Economic Times |publisher=Economictimes.indiatimes.com |date=2012-08-06 |accessdate=2013-09-28 |archive-date=2014-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311130750/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/news-by-industry/transportation/railways/delhi-metro-to-link-up-with-rapid-rail/articleshow/15372304.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[德里地铁|德里地铁]]的单程票和IC卡可以在古尔冈快速地铁系统中使用。<ref>{{cite web |author=TNN 14 Sep 2012, 01.51AM IST |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-09-14/gurgaon/33843097_1_rapid-metro-rail-gurgaon-delhi-metro-commuters-shankar-chowk |title=Gurgaon rapid Metro ready for trials |publisher=Articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2012-09-14 |accessdate=2013-09-28 |archive-date=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231064149/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-09-14/gurgaon/33843097_1_rapid-metro-rail-gurgaon-delhi-metro-commuters-shankar-chowk |dead-url=yes }}</ref>自动收费系统由[[泰雷兹集团|泰雷兹集团]]提供。<ref>{{cite web|title=Technology|url=http://rapidmetrogurgaon.com/theprojectTechnology.aspx|work=Rapid Metro Gurgaon|accessdate=2014-02-06|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209232109/http://rapidmetrogurgaon.com/theprojectTechnology.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===间隔与运营时间===
古尔冈快速地铁的运营时间为06:05至22:00<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rapidmetrogurgaon.com/theprojectQuickFact.aspx |title=Quick facts |publisher=unknown |accessdate=2016-06-08 |archive-date=2016-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403041857/http://rapidmetrogurgaon.com/theprojectQuickFact.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，间隔为4分钟。列车最高速度80km/h，平均旅速40km/h。<ref name="toi">{{cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-07-16/delhi/28184665_1_metro-link-cyber-city-dlf |title=Gurgaon metro link to be completed in 30 months |newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |date=2009-07-16 |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archive-date=2012-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024074803/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-07-16/delhi/28184665_1_metro-link-cyber-city-dlf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

